{"tid":2366180,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港寬頻認按國安法要求封「香港編年史」網站","createTime":"2021-01-14T09:48:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-14T16:46:05.000Z","uid":291865,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3df8a036378ba83c0a3ae21baf93640d8acb8ba9","tid":2366180,"uid":291865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T09:48:49.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】香港寬頻承認是按國安法要求，停止連線到「香港編年史」網站。<br />\n<br />\n香港寬頻表示，相關網站連線是於星期三下午起停止，是首間網絡供應商承認按國安法要求封鎖網站。<br />\n<br />\n「香港編年史」網站有多名建制派人士和警員資料，網站主編及管理人早前發聲明指，由上周三起就收到報告，指使用部分香港網絡供應商服務時，無法連線到網站。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=420293\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D420293&d=qXcR1A%2FTALq%2FhnoNE0cJVQZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=38081819\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D420293&h=8fa8506b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=420293</a>"},{"pid":"912d97b1a1c1cbfcc31c94ce9ca368c9b771dd27","tid":2366180,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3df8a036378ba83c0a3ae21baf93640d8acb8ba9","tid":2366180,"uid":291865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T09:48:49.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】香港寬頻承認是按國安法要求，停止連線到「香港編年史」網站。<br />\n<br />\n香港寬頻表示，相關網站連線是於星期三下午起停止，是首間網絡供應商承認按國安法要求封鎖網站。<br />\n<br />\n「香港編年史」網站有多名建制派人士和警員資料，網站主編及管理人早前發聲明指，由上周三起就收到報告，指使用部分香港網絡供應商服務時，無法連線到網站。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=420293\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D420293&d=qXcR1A%2FTALq%2FhnoNE0cJVQZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=38081819\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D420293&h=8fa8506b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=420293</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime